{
  "_comment": "GOAT Squad BASEBALL config — everything game-specific for goatsquad-baseball.html (clone of the goatsquad.html engine with a field layout + baseball series sim). Data comes from squadball-mlb.json (bake with `node fetch-squadball.js` — it also patches mlbamId onto the gauntlet rosters + managers below). Slots carry x/y (percent) coords for the on-field layout; the manager sits in the dugout.",
